headline: Check your freezer for this Blue Bell ice cream sold at Walmart and Kroger, recalled over serious life-threatening risk
summary: Half-gallons of this frozen treat flavor are being pulled off shelves in 16 states, according to a notice from the FDA.

headline: Alpha Modus Files Patent Infringement Lawsuit Against Cooler Screens
summary: CORNELIUS, N.C., Aug. 25, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Alpha Modus Holdings Inc.
